      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: \"هُلْكٌ بِذَوِي اَلْمُرُوءَةِ أَنْ يَبِيتَ اَلرَّجُلُ عَنْ مَنْزِلِهِ بِالْمِصْرِ اَلَّذِي فِيهِ أَهْلُهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4906 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"It is a disgrace for a man of dignity to spend the night away from his home in the city where his family resides.\""
        ]
      }
